3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes modifications to the transmitter and receiver for improving the performance of 5G NR, which can be considered as a control system. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper proposes a modification to the error correction scheme for 5G NR, which can be considered as a networking architecture. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): Although the paper does not explicitly mention any data structures or algorithms, the proposed modification to the polar code can be considered as an algorithmic improvement.
